Tata’s Jaguar Land Rover Mulling U.K. Plant, Telegraph Says

-- B y   T h o m a s   B i e s h e u v e l
-- 
2011-04-24T10:19:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-24/tata-s-jaguar-land-rover-mulling-u-k-plant-telegraph-says.html
Tata Motors Ltd. (TTMT) ’s Jaguar Land
Rover is considering building an engine plant in the U.K. that
could create more than 1,000 jobs, the Sunday Telegraph
reported, citing sources close to the company.  The company could base the plant in Wolverhampton, South
Wales or an unnamed site in  India , the newspaper said. An
announcement could be made within the next month, the Sunday
Telegraph reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Thomas Biesheuvel in London at 
 tbiesheuvel@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
